WEBVTT

00:02.000 --> 00:03.719
Carys! Carys!

00:03.719 --> 00:06.119
My mum killed herself and I think
that it has something to do

00:06.120 --> 00:10.320
with your daughter, Carys. 23 years
gone and you lot are still at it.

00:11.880 --> 00:13.919
You're my mother!
And I'm your daughter!

00:13.920 --> 00:15.439
I don't want you.

00:15.440 --> 00:18.879
What have you done to her?
Aron. What have you done?

00:18.880 --> 00:20.639
Dad? What's happened?

00:20.640 --> 00:23.039
Let's keep this our secret.

00:23.040 --> 00:25.080
If only Matilda could
remember something.

00:26.440 --> 00:27.919
Like who took her.

00:27.920 --> 00:30.479
He gazed into a mirror,
a black mirror.

00:30.480 --> 00:32.759
He thought he was talking to angels.

00:32.759 --> 00:36.919
I feel like there's something in me,
scared of what I'm going to see.

00:36.920 --> 00:39.239
You can't look away.
And keep watching the mirror.

00:39.240 --> 00:41.439
No matter what, I'll be right here.

00:41.440 --> 00:43.279
That's what the voice said.

00:43.280 --> 00:46.360
She's trapped in a field
of yellow flowers.

